      "acceptanceCriteria": "Continuum FEA with nonlinear geometry and frictional contact; constitutive model validated against coupon data for Ti-6Al-4V rod and screw alloy.",
      "rationale": "Nonlinear continuum FEA with large-deformation kinematics and penalty-based frictional contact captures the dominant load-transfer mechanisms. Bilinear isotropic hardening calibrated against published Ti-6Al-4V tensile coupon data. Model form judged appropriate for the compression-bending regime of ASTM F1717."
