      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties sourced from certified mill certificates or peer-reviewed literature; geometric dimensions from CMM measurements of test specimens.",
      "rationale": "Elastic modulus and yield strength for the rod (Ti-6Al-4V ELI) taken from mill certificates for the test lot. Screw geometry digitized via CMM with 5 µm resolution. Friction coefficient for titanium-on-titanium contact set to 0.3 per published tribology literature. Sensitivity analysis on friction (0.2–0.4) showed <3% effect on stiffness QoI."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test samples",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
