      "rationale": "Eleven constructs assembled from production-representative screws and rods. CMM inspection confirmed all critical dimensions within drawing tolerances. Two independent laboratories contributed specimens, providing inter-laboratory variability data. Sample size sufficient to estimate mean and standard deviation for Bayesian validation metric."
