      "acceptanceCriteria": "Simulation inputs (geometry, material, boundary conditions) demonstrably match physical test setup; documented traceability matrix provided.",
      "rationale": "Traceability matrix maps each simulation input to its experimental counterpart. Boundary conditions replicate F1717 fixture kinematics (pin-pin end conditions). Torque applied to set screws in simulation matched to torque wrench values recorded during experimental assembly. No unmatched parameters identified."
