      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison using E/uval metric; acceptance threshold E/uval < 1.96 and percent difference < 10% for all three QoIs.",
      "rationale": "E/uval computed for stiffness (0.84), yield force (1.21), and force at 40 mm (1.09), all below the 1.96 threshold. Percent differences were 4.2%, 6.8%, and 5.1% respectively, all within the 10% bound. Validation metric passed for all three QoIs."
    },
